  "title": "Central Kitchen Manager #81761",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing/ Food Production</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Central Kitchen Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Senoko</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon – Fri, 8am – 5pm; Sat, 8am – 12pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic $8,000 - $10,000 + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for coordinating and controlling production processes to maintain output and reduce waste.</li><li>Develop and put in place safety rules and standards to provide a safe workplace for all employees.</li><li>Train, supervise, and manage central kitchen staff to ensure work is done correctly and efficiently.</li><li>Handle non-compliance issues when needed in a professional and timely manner.</li><li>Carry out other duties or projects assigned by the Director.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 5 years of relevant experience managing central kitchen operations.</li><li>Strong experience overseeing large-scale food production.</li><li>Familiar with the Workplace Safety and Health (WSH) Act.</li><li>Working knowledge of Microsoft Office is required.</li><li>Proficient in English; ability to communicate with Mandarin-speaking stakeholders for work purposes is an advantage.</li><li>Willing to travel when required.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81761 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
